<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en-US" dir="ltr">
<head>
  <%- include('../../partials/header.ejs'); %>

  <style>
    .groupTitle {
        font-size: 1em;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-top: 1em;
        margin-bottom: 0.5em;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-lane);
        margin-left: -1em;
        margin-right: -1em;
        background: var(--color-lane);
        padding: 1em;
        border-radius: 3px;
        position: relative;
    }
    .groupTitle .groupNumber{
        font-size: .7em;
        padding: 0.5em 1em;
        margin-right: 0.5em;
        display: inline-block;
        border-radius: 2.5em;
        background: var(--color-pop);
        color: var(--color-body);
    }
    .groupTitle .groupNote{
        font-size: .875em;
        font-weight: 400;
        color: var(--color-body-subtitle);
        letter-spacing: 1px;
        margin-bottom: 1em;
    }
    .groupScroll{
        position: absolute;
        right: -1.5em;
        font-size: 1em;
        color: var(--color-pop);
        transition: all .5s ease;
    }
    .groupScroll:hover,.groupScroll:active,.groupScroll:focus{
        color: var(--color-pop-h);
    }
    .councilPersonImg{
        height: 250px;
        width: 250px;
        min-width: 250px;
        background-size: cover;
        border-radius: 50%;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 50;
        background-color: var(--color-pop);
        border: 20px solid var(--color-body);
    }
    .councilPerson {
        background: var(--color-chrome);
        padding: 1em;
        box-shadow: var(--shadow-standard-y);
        border-radius: 3px;
        margin-left: -125px;
        padding-left: calc(125px + 1em);
        width: 100%;
    }
    .councilWrapper{
        display: flex;
        justify-content: flex-start;
        align-items: center;
        margin-bottom: 1em;
    }
    .councilPersonData p{
        margin-bottom: 0;
    }
    .councilPersonData h3{
        font-size: 1.5em;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: var(--color-body-text);
    }
    .councilPersonData {
        justify-content: center;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
    }
    .councilPersonQuestions {
        background: var(--color-body);
        padding: 1em;
        border-radius: 3px;
    }
    .councilPersonQuestions h4{
        font-size: 1em;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: var(--color-body-text);
        margin: 0;
    }
    ul > li {
        margin-bottom: 0.5em;
        font-size: .875em;
    }
    a{
        color: var(--color-pop);
        transition: all .5s ease;
    }
    a:hover,a:focus,a:active{
        color: var(--color-pop-h);
    }
    .compact .councilWrapper{

    }
    .compact .councilPersonQuestions{
        display: none;
    }
    @media screen and (max-width: 39.9375em) {
        .councilWrapper {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        }
        .councilPerson {
        margin-left: 0;
        padding-left: 1em;
        width: 100%;
        margin-top: -1em;
        }
        .councilPersonData{
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 1em;
        }
        .councilPersonQuestions{
            padding: 0;
            background: transparent
        }
        .groupScroll{
            display: none;
        }
        .groupTitle{
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            text-align: center;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .groupNumber{
            width: auto;
            width: fit-content;
            margin-top: -2em;
        }
  }


  </style>
  <script defer type="text/javascript" src="/js/pages/staff-council.js"></script>
</head>
<%- include('../../partials/layout/top.ejs'); %>
<% const staffData = JSON.parse(include('staffdata.ejs')); 

const groupBy = (items, key) => items.reduce(
  (result, item) => ({
    ...result,
    [item[key]]: [
      ...(result[item[key]] || []),
      item,
    ],
  }), 
  {},
);

const GroupedStaff = groupBy(staffData,'Group')
%>

<div class="help-page staffVoting">
    <div class="grid-container fluid swim-lane">
      <div class="grid-container">
        <h1 id="top">Staff Council - Voting Companion</h1>
        <div class="cell small-12" style="justify-content: flex-end;display: flex;margin-top:-2em">
            <div class="switch">
                <input class="switch-input" id="compactMode" type="checkbox" name="compactMode">
                <label class="switch-paddle" for="compactMode">
                  <span class="switch-active" aria-hidden="true"><i class="fas fa-user-circle"></i></span>
                  <span class="switch-inactive" aria-hidden="true"><i class="fas fa-address-card"></i></span>
                </label>
              </div>
        </div>
        <div class="grid-x grid-margin-x">
            <div class="cell small-12 medium-6">
                <p>The WPI Staff Council is the voice of the employees at the university. Members are elected by their peers to advocate for and act as a collective voice for the interests and needs of WPIâ€™s non-union staff. Having a staff council helps foster a positive and inclusive environment at WPI and offers an informed support and resource for staff members.</p>
                <p>The elections for the inaugural Staff Council are opening this week. Online ballots will open on Wednesday, July 20, and will close for voting on July 29.</p>
                <p>For more information about the Staff Council, see the <a href="https://www.wpi.edu/offices/talent/employee-resources/staff-council" target="_blank">Staff Council webpage</a>.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="cell small-12 medium-6">
                <ul data-smooth-scroll data-offset="150" class="no-bullet">
                    <li><strong>Quick Links</strong></li>
                    <li><a href="#group1">Group 1 - Advancement, OGC, and Talent & Inclusion</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#group2">Group 2 - Finance & Operations (Budget & Operations, Campus Safety, Controller's Office, and Campus Planning & Facilities Management)</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#group3">Group 3 - Chief of Staff, Marketing Communications, and Undergraduate Enrollment</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#group4">Group 4 - Finance & Operations (Information Technology)</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#group5">Group 5 - Provost Office (Office Operations-Provost, Budget & IT- Provost, CPBL and GPS, Undergraduate Studies, Faculty Governance, and Graduate Studies)</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#group6">Group 6 - Provost Office (Academic & Corporate Engagement, Innovation & Entrepreneurship, Research Division, Library Services, and Registrar)</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#group7">Group 7 - Provost Office (Global School, School of Arts & Sciences, School Of Business, and School of Engineering)</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#group8">Group 8 - Student Affairs</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</div>
  <% for(const [key,value] of Object.entries(GroupedStaff)){%>
    <div class="grid-container fluid swim-lane">
      <div class="grid-container">
        <div class="grid-x grid-margin-x">
            <div class="cell small-12">
                <% const group = {};
                group.number = key.split(":")[0];
                group.name = key.includes(":") ? key.split(":")[1].split("(")[0] : null;
                group.note =  key.includes("(") ? "(" + key.split(":")[1].split("(")[1].slice(0, -1) + ")" : null;
                %>

                <h2 class="groupTitle" id="<%=group.number.replace(/ /g, "").toLowerCase()%>"><span class="groupNumber"><%=group.number%></span><span class="groupName"><%=group.name%></span><span class="groupNote"><%=group.note%></span><a class="groupScroll" href="#top" title="Scroll to Top of Page" data-smooth-scroll><i class="fas fa-chevron-up"></i></a></h2>


            </div>
            <div class="cell small-12 grid-x">
                <% value.sort((a, b) => (a.Name.split(' ').pop() > b.Name.split(' ').pop()) ? 1 : -1) %> 

                <%for(person of value){%>
                    
                    <% 
                    var imgURL = ''
                    if(person["Picture File Name"] != ''){
                        imgURL = "background-image:url('img/staffCouncil/" + person["Picture File Name"] + ".jpg')"
                    }
                    %>
                    <div class="cell small-12 medium-12 councilWrapper">
                            <div class="councilPersonImg" style="<%=imgURL%>"></div>
                            <div class="councilPerson grid-x">
                                <div class="cell small-12 medium-3 councilPersonData">
                                    <h3><%=person.Name%></h3>
                                    <p class="councilPersonTitle"><%=person["Business Title"]%></p>
                                    <p class="councilPersonEmail"><a href="mailto:<%=person['Contact Information']%>"><i class="fad fa-envelope"></i> <%=person['Contact Information']%></a></p>
                                    <p class="councilPersonTenure"><%=parseFloat(person["Tenure (in Years)"].toFixed(1))%> years at WPI</p>
                                </div>

                                <div class="cell small-12 medium-9 councilPersonQuestions">
                                    <%if(person["What do you hope to achieve as a member of the Staff Council?"] != ''){%>
                                        <h4>What do you hope to achieve as a member of the Staff Council?</h4>
                                        <p><%-person["What do you hope to achieve as a member of the Staff Council?"]%></p>
                                    <%}%>
                                    <%if(person["What do you believe the Staff Council should focus on to support the staff experience and voice at WPI?"] != ''){%>
                                        <h4>What do you believe the Staff Council should focus on to support the staff experience and voice at WPI?</h4>
                                        <p><%-person["What do you believe the Staff Council should focus on to support the staff experience and voice at WPI?"]%></p>
                                    <%}%>
                                    <%if(person["What would you like people to know about you as a candidate for Staff Council?"] != ''){%>
                                        <h4>What would you like people to know about you as a candidate for Staff Council?</h4>
                                        <p><%-person["What would you like people to know about you as a candidate for Staff Council?"]%></p>
                                    <%}%>
                                    <%if(person["What is your favorite hobby, movie, song, fun fact, and/or quote?"] != ''){%>
                                        <h4>What is your favorite hobby, movie, song, fun fact, and/or quote?</h4>
                                        <p><%-person["What is your favorite hobby, movie, song, fun fact, and/or quote?"]%></p>
                                    <%}%>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                    </div>
                <%}%>
            </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <%}%>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="grid-x grid-margin-x">
      <div class="cell small-12">
        
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
<%- include('../../partials/layout/bottom.ejs'); %>
</html>